About this home

Like 2 homes in one!! This spacious luxury home has approx 4,800 square feet located on a very nice cul-de-sac. Almost 3,300 square feet two story above grade and there is approx 1,400 square feet of finished basement accessed from inside and has a separate outside entrance. 47' long room for recreation/gaming/theatre or simply lounging. There is a separate room 16 x 11 room with closet that is currently being used like a 5th bedroom but not officially a bedroom since this room does not have a window. There is a nice area for another refrigerator and microwave to create a kitchenette. 4 bedrooms are upstairs with the primary bedroom offering a 19' luxury bathroom and 16x10 GIANT walk-in closet room. Professional photography scheduled to be taken early afternoon on Tuesday, Dec. 2nd. Should be uploaded by that evening. Feel free to drive by but must then make appointment for viewing.

If you opt out on this website, your choice will not apply to any other Redfin site, and you will need to separately opt-out on those sites. Similarly, your opt out will only apply to the device on which you opt out, and only for so long as you maintain cookies on the device. Therefore, you must opt out on each device separately (or, if you clear cookies, on the same device) when you visit our website. If you choose to opt out of the “sale” or "sharing" of your personal information, you may continue to see advertising, such as ads by us or our partners related to you and your interests, including, for example, ads that do not involve the “sale” or "sharing" of personal information.
